{"type":null,"faqId":49871,"title":"华为智能手表_佩戴不锈钢编织带款的注意事项？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body12614887\"><ol id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__ol7744859\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__li46425119\">请保持表带水平插入卡扣。<span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c51e_3xuar.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__li2338313\">确保卡扣上的金属凸起部分平滑地在表带内面凹槽内移动。<span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c51f_jy2zf.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></li></ol><div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__note2594873\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c520_naodu.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__ul55185655\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__li26908851\">超出凹槽区域时应及时取出，<strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__b40853074\">请勿扣合</strong>。否则会对表带造成不可逆的损害。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329058__li32133347\">如果扣合卡扣时需要较大力度，建议微调表带再扣合。</li></ul></div></div></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":494,"faqType":"维护与保养","useful":4,"unUseful":5,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329058","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Product-Maintenance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615861000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":89,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"不锈钢，编织带，注意","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}